		<div class='css_post_message'>Hi Chris, I used to work with Amy at Portofino Medical Spa. My heart goes out to you both and I will put you on our church (Cokesbury) prayer list. My husband and I went through a tough time for 9 months when he was miss-diagnosed as well. We finally went to Oshners in New Orleans and they immediately figured out what was wrong. I had questioned the Dr.s here in Pensacola over and over and they all said the same thing----"oh thats NOT it". With out going into too much detail, after many different specialists, and tons of very invasive testing, no one could find the right answer. Oshners found it immediately and guess what---I was right all along! My poor husband was sick in the bed over 9 months.It was right after our son was born. Talk about tough! Having an infant and a sick husband! After Oshners, he was 100% healthy after 2 weeks! My point is ,I am sorry, but Dr.s dont know anything! Listen to your body, get a 2nd, 3rd, 4th opinion! I will pray for you and your family and remember to please lean on God  right now----the only thing that got us through that crazy 9 months was our FAITH. </div>
